        {
            "title": "有片｜屯門公路兩私家車風馳電掣  入彎疑「甩尾」相撞同死火 冒白煙一司機送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/50ae4e9aebf471efadac97c6360c0102/5788ec4f30934861b09b9412d599f32d-32e25d5846922fc13a9eae4383e00f1d-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67b1261ac3cc2\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67b1261ac3cc3\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ffe0255eab34b2dc971a38600b0f03cf/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250216/_2025021607373035428.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>屯門公路今日凌晨發生車禍。網上流傳影片顯示，一輛深色私家車和一輛白色私家車沿屯門公路往荃灣方向高速飛馳，且發出巨大引擎聲，未幾即在一彎位相撞，同車同時死火，白色私家車更煙出大量白煙，司機及乘客急忙跳車。\n\n</p><h2>一陣巨大引擎聲後  兩車「騎住」快線與中線疾駛而過</h2>\n<p>根據來自同一個車主的3段「車cam」影片，事件發生在凌晨零時24分左右，當時cam主的車在慢線行駛，突然傳來一陣巨大引擎聲，一輛深色私家「騎」在右邊快線與中線疾駛而過，一輛白色私家車緊貼其後，兩車如箭般飆前，即將消失在盡頭彎位時，突然見到兩車似乎相撞，然後冒出滾滾白煙。第一段車cam至此結束。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4082920/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"cam主的車在慢線行駛，突然傳來一陣巨大引擎聲，一輛深色私家「騎」在右邊快線與中線疾駛而過。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8531758630ed2168cb7d3772c4e964a3/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-15_at_10_39_57_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        cam主的車在慢線行駛，突然傳來一陣巨大引擎聲，一輛深色私家「騎」在右邊快線與中線疾駛而過。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4082921/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一輛白色私家車緊貼其後。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/da12eeb00e175e4e2d6545b7394f82cd/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-15_at_10_40_06_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一輛白色私家車緊貼其後。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4082927/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"兩車如箭般飆前，即將消失在盡頭彎位。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bc58cf45aea294626d43e27306a6b746/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-15_at_10_40_08_PM_0.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        兩車如箭般飆前，即將消失在盡頭彎位。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4082923/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"突然見到兩車似乎相撞，然後冒出滾滾白煙。第一段車cam至此結束。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2c401ae407886d0c5e861a66bc3c2760/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-15_at_10_40_11_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        突然見到兩車似乎相撞，然後冒出滾滾白煙。第一段車cam至此結束。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4082924/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"第二段車cam片，cam主的車繼續向前行， 見到有汽車零件散落路面上，深色私家車打死火燈停在快線，白色私家車則停在路肩，有幾名青年落了車。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4f08f7442a40b4459cf64171f277daae/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-15_at_10_41_27_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        第二段車cam片，cam主的車繼續向前行， 見到有汽車零件散落路面上，深色私家車打死火燈停在快線，白色私家車則停在路肩，有幾名青年落了車。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4082925/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"深色私家車打死火燈停在快線。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e727f7b59838e809d2ddf469987a4755/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-15_at_10_42_08_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        深色私家車打死火燈停在快線。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4082926/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"有汽車零件散落路面上。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b8cfb0fde7f28fa785a6b14921b6d240/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-15_at_10_43_03_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        有汽車零件散落路面上。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>第二段車cam片，cam主的車繼續向前行， 見到有汽車零件散落路面上，深色私家車打死火燈停在快線，白色私家車則停在路肩，有幾名青年落了車。事件中，懷疑深色私家車高速行駛時「甩尾」，撞到白色私家車肇事。\n\n</p>\n<p>警方表示，今日（16日）凌晨零時34分接獲報案，兩輛私家車前後沿屯門公路往荃灣方向行駛，途經一間國際學校對開時，前車懷疑失控撞向後車，車上27歲馮姓男司機眼部受傷，清醒送往屯門醫院接受治理。後車的24歲姓陳男司機沒有受傷。事故中沒有車輛起火，警方正調查車禍原因。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2053039/即時-港聞-有片-屯門公路兩私家車風馳電掣-入彎疑-甩尾-相撞同死火-冒白煙一司機送院",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-16 07:41:15",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "異食癖｜陝西女生連吃6年膠袋 胃裡取出1公斤塑料",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"陝西女生連吃6年膠袋，胃裡取出1公斤塑料。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/fbc1b64eca5f821d617a137c8e17086b/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250215/_2025021516220979715.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">陝西女生連吃6年膠袋，胃裡取出1公斤塑料。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>在陝西西安，近日有一名女子腹痛去醫院求診，醫生檢查後赫然發現，她的胃裡堆積密密麻麻的塑膠袋碎片，總重達1公斤，醫生指，女子吞膠袋長達6年，恐已罹患「異食癖」。\n\n</p><h2>從12歲吃到18歲</h2>\n<p>綜合內媒報道，西安市紅會醫院近日收治了一位患有異食癖的女生。患者18歲，從12歲開始食用膠袋，6年期間吃了大量塑料，造成腸梗阻。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3362917/%E9%A3%9F%E9%A0%AD%E9%AB%AE3%E5%B9%B4%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B111%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9%E6%82%A3%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%BB%E7%97%85%E8%83%83%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%96%E5%87%BA38cm%E9%95%B7%E5%B7%A8%E6%AF%9B%E7%9F%B3\">食頭髮3年｜廣東11歲女孩患「公主病」　胃中取出38cm長「巨毛石」</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4081890/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"醫生從陝西女生胃裡取出1公斤塑料。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8231b98f095589988955ca557d98743a/2025-02/vlcsnap-2025-02-15-12h45m14s670.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        醫生從陝西女生胃裡取出1公斤塑料。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4081891/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"醫生檢查赫然發現女子腸胃中堆積大量膠袋碎片，無法消化。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0e5976777c4d4771543ec9a225eaf089/2025-02/vlcsnap-2025-02-15-12h45m23s179.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        醫生檢查赫然發現女子腸胃中堆積大量膠袋碎片，無法消化。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4081892/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"醫生在內鏡下用9小時取出胃中的異物。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0046052fe550af65e75a4b9369249f59/2025-02/vlcsnap-2025-02-15-12h45m34s638.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        醫生在內鏡下用9小時取出胃中的異物。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4081893/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"醫生在內鏡下用9小時取出胃中的異物。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/07f127181afc88b8be7dba3dc3acfead/2025-02/vlcsnap-2025-02-15-12h45m53s347.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        醫生在內鏡下用9小時取出胃中的異物。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4081894/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"女子從12歲就開始吞食塑膠袋，已吃了6年，醫生從其胃裡取出1公斤塑料。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f152c4b382e624bcc23c922b74aa13bb/2025-02/vlcsnap-2025-02-15-12h46m03s269.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女子從12歲就開始吞食塑膠袋，已吃了6年，醫生從其胃裡取出1公斤塑料。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4081895/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"醫生在內鏡下用9小時取出胃中的異物。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/72a0fcbb8ef8142ce1785c379f04e57e/2025-02/vlcsnap-2025-02-15-12h46m09s046.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        醫生在內鏡下用9小時取出胃中的異物。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p>消化內科副主任醫生施育鵬介紹，患者因腹痛無法排便來就診，檢查赫然發現女子腸胃中堆積大量膠袋碎片，無法消化，已呈現褐色，決定動三次手術取出。最終，醫生在內鏡下用9小時取出胃中的異物，重量約1公斤。目前患者狀態平穩，膠袋碎片已全部取出。\n\n</p>\n<p>醫生透露，這名女子從12歲就開始吞食塑膠袋，已吃了6年，恐已罹患「異食癖」，而她治療後目前狀況良好。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3172165/%E9%99%9D%E8%A5%BF%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E9%A0%AD%E9%AB%AE%E7%A8%80%E7%96%8F%E7%84%A1%E9%A3%9F%E6%85%BE%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2-%E5%89%96%E8%85%B9%E9%A9%9A%E8%A6%8B3%E5%85%AC%E6%96%A4%E6%AF%9B%E7%90%83\">陝西少女頭髮稀疏無食慾送院 剖腹驚見3公斤「毛球」</a></strong>\n</p>\n<p>事實上，異食癖案例時有所聞，東莞市一名11歲女童，去年因腹部劇痛前往醫院就診，醫生檢查後赫然發現，她的胃和腸管裡有大塊毛絮狀結石，幾乎塞滿整個胃，於是耗時近1小時的腹腔鏡手術，從其胃中取出一塊38cm長、15cm寬、10cm厚的堅硬毛髮結石。她的父母透露，3年前就發現女兒喜歡拔頭髮吃，屢勸不聽，醫生表示，喜食異物恐是生活習慣、行為及心理出問題，要及時就診。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
